OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777986670
OL,3,CFood prices set to rise by 50% on
OL,4,Cstart of cost-of-living crisis by
OL,5,CNovember
OL,7,FUK food prices are on track to be 50%
OL,8,Fhigher by November compared to levels
OL,9,Fat the start of the cost-of-living
OL,10,Fcrisis in mid-2021, according to
OL,11,Fresearch.
OL,13,FThe "grim milestone" would mean that
OL,14,Fthe price growth seen in the nearly 20
OL,15,Fyears prior to the crisis would be
OL,16,Fachieved in just over five years `
OL,17,Falmost quadrupling the pace of food
OL,18,Finflation, the Energy and Climate
OL,19,FIntelligence Unit (ECIU) think tank
OL,20,Fsaid.
OL,26,@uD@EOUuD@TO]
