OL,3,CFood prices set to rise by 50% on
OL,4,Cstart of cost-of-living crisis by
OL,5,CNovember
OL,7,FA combination of extreme weather
OL,8,Fdriven by climate change, global
OL,9,Fsupply disruptions, and continued
OL,10,Fexposure to volatile oil and gas
OL,11,Fmarkets had compounded pressures on
OL,12,Fthe food system.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
