PN,31805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777986670
OL,3,CFood prices set to rise by 50% on
OL,4,Cstart of cost-of-living crisis by
OL,5,CNovember
OL,7,FChris Jaccarini, food and farming
OL,8,Fanalyst at the ECIU, said: "Trump's
OL,9,Fwar in the Middle East is set to drive
OL,10,Fshopping bills higher as oil and gas
OL,11,Fprices spike.
OL,13,F"Scientists are predicting 2027 to be
OL,14,Fthe hottest year on record with
OL,15,Fclimate change combining with the El
OL,16,FNino effect kicking off this year.
OL,17,FThree of England's worst harvests on
OL,18,Frecord have been in the past five
OL,19,Fyears.
OL,26,@pD@\OUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
