OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777986670
OL,3,CFood prices set to rise by 50% on
OL,4,Cstart of cost-of-living crisis by
OL,5,CNovember
OL,7,F"Unless we get to net zero emissions
OL,8,Fto stop climate change and bring
OL,9,Fbalance to the system, food prices
OL,10,Fwill spiral ever further, but net zero
OL,11,Falso means burning less oil and gas,
OL,12,Fso insulating our food system from the
OL,13,Fkind of price spikes we've been seeing
OL,14,Fsince Russian invaded Ukraine."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
