OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777986670
OL,3,CFood prices set to rise by 50% on
OL,4,Cstart of cost-of-living crisis by
OL,5,CNovember
OL,7,FThe ECIU said the projected 50%
OL,8,Fincrease would mean that many
OL,9,Fhouseholds would continue to feel the
OL,10,Fstrain well beyond the initial phase
OL,11,Fof the cost-of-living crisis, with
OL,12,Ffood remaining one of the most visible
OL,13,Fand unavoidable expenses.
OL,15,FAnna Taylor, executive director of the
OL,16,FFood Foundation, said: "Food prices
OL,17,Frising this high and this fast leaves
OL,18,Ffamilies on the lowest incomes with
OL,19,Fnowhere left to cut except the food on
OL,20,Ftheir plate.
OL,26,@xD@XOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777986670
OL,3,CFood prices set to rise by 50% on
OL,4,Cstart of cost-of-living crisis by
OL,5,CNovember
OL,7,F"When that happens, people skip meals,
OL,8,Fchildren go hungry, and diet-related
OL,9,Fillness rises ` taking parents out of
OL,10,Fwork and piling pressure on an NHS
OL,11,Fthat can least afford it.
OL,13,F"This conflict is the latest shock in
OL,14,Fa series, and there will be more. The
OL,15,Fquestion for Government isn't just how
OL,16,Fto respond to this crisis ` it's
OL,17,Fwhether we're finally going to build a
OL,18,Ffood system resilient enough to
OL,19,Fwithstand the next one."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU{D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
