PN,31810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777986670
OL,3,CFood prices set to rise by 50% on
OL,4,Cstart of cost-of-living crisis by
OL,5,CNovember
OL,7,FDespite this, food waste ranks fifth
OL,8,Famong key concerns, after food prices,
OL,9,Fdiet healthiness, animal welfare, and
OL,10,Fprocessed or ultra-processed foods,
OL,11,F"suggesting it is more of a background
OL,12,Fconcern than a top-of-mind issue",
OL,13,FWrap said.
OL,15,FConcerns that have increased most
OL,16,Fsince 2024 include pesticide use, how
OL,17,Ffood producers and farmers are
OL,18,Ftreated, genetically modified foods,
OL,19,Fand hormones, steroids, and
OL,20,Fantibiotics in food.
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@aO]
