OL,3,CFood prices set to rise by 50% on
OL,4,Cstart of cost-of-living crisis by
OL,5,CNovember
OL,7,FWrap chief executive Catherine David
OL,8,Fsaid: "The average household of four
OL,9,Fspends a whopping #1,000 each year on
OL,10,Fgood food that goes in the bin and
OL,11,Fcould have been eaten."
